our website too!<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"tve-droppable\">What&#8217;s Changed?<\/h2>\n<h3 class=\"tve-droppable\">1. The Look.<\/h3>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">Here&#8217;s a side-by-side comparison of our old and new site designs:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-0b7d94d elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"0b7d94d\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-758871d\" data-id=\"758871d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8773f3f elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8773f3f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"371\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/03\/screencapture-micepadapp-2019-03-12-17_41_08-371x1024.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2310\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/03\/screencapture-micepadapp-2019-03-12-17_41_08-371x1024.png 371w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/03\/screencapture-micepadapp-2019-03-12-17_41_08-109x300.png 109w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/03\/screencapture-micepadapp-2019-03-12-17_41_08-556x1536.png 556w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/03\/screencapture-micepadapp-2019-03-12-17_41_08.png 724w\" sizes